==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: tiān xíng jiàn, jūnzĭ yĭ zìqiángbùxí
===Etymology===
From the [[I Ching]] ([[易經]])

===Proverb===
'''[[天]][[行]][[健]]，[[君子]][[以]][[自強不息]]'''
# Just as the celestial bodies never run out of energy to orbit round and round, so to should we strive unendingly to better ourselves.
===Alternate forms===
[[天行健，君子以自强不息]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
